OL,3,CThe post-election blame game has
OL,4,Cstarted - and Starmer is the only loser
OL,6,FThe post-election blame game has
OL,7,Fstarted. And there is only one loser:
OL,8,FKeir Starmer.
OL,10,F"Voters don't hate the party," said
OL,11,Fone minister. "They hate Keir."
OL,13,FResults so far have ignited Labour
OL,14,FMPs' darkest fears, namely that Reform
OL,15,Fis on course to win the next general
OL,16,Felection.
OL,18,F"That is down to Starmer," said the
OL,19,Fminister. "There is no glossing that.
OL,20,FIt's what we all hear on the doorstep,
OL,21,Ffrom voters."
