OL,3,CThe post-election blame game has
OL,4,Cstarted - and Starmer is the only loser
OL,6,FWhat is particularly electric is that
OL,7,FReform trounced Labour in Burnham-and-
OL,8,FRayner land, Greater Manchester.
OL,10,FReform had an almost clean sweep in
OL,11,FTameside, Angela Rayner's manor, and
OL,12,FWigan, Lisa Nandy's domain, which is
OL,13,Fpart of Andy Burnham's Greater
OL,14,FManchester Combined Authority.
OL,16,FThe personal local brands of Burnham
OL,17,Fand Rayner, both potential successors
OL,18,Fto Starmer, were overwhelmed by
OL,19,FFarage's.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
