OL,3,CThe post-election blame game has
OL,4,Cstarted - and Starmer is the only loser
OL,6,FBut that does not mean they will
OL,7,Fabandon their ambitions to lead their
OL,8,Fparty.
OL,10,FQuite the contrary.
OL,12,FThey will blame Starmer for the
OL,13,Fhumiliation. The question is how far
OL,14,Fthey will articulate that in public.
OL,16,FAs for Starmer, he says he takes
OL,17,Fresponsibility for the debacle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
