CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778270754
OL,3,CThe post-election blame game has
OL,4,Cstarted - and Starmer is the only loser
OL,6,FAlthough it is a funny kind of
OL,7,Fresponsibility because he says he is
OL,8,Fgoing nowhere, and will attempt to
OL,9,Frespond to voters' rejection of Labour
OL,10,Fwith deeds and words to woo them back.
OL,12,FStrikingly, the foreign secretary
OL,13,FYvette Cooper just told the BBC that
OL,14,Fthe debacle is a collective failure of
OL,15,Fthe whole cabinet, and they all have
OL,16,Fto search their souls - in effect -
OL,17,Fabout how to respond.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
