OL,3,CThe post-election blame game has
OL,4,Cstarted - and Starmer is the only loser
OL,6,FThis was not the foreign secretary
OL,7,Fsaying she stands by Starmer in all
OL,8,Fweathers, though I presume many will
OL,9,Fhave heard it that way.
OL,11,FWhat I heard was a message to her
OL,12,Fcabinet colleagues that they need to
OL,13,Fthink very hard about what has been
OL,14,Fgoing wrong and not lemming-like
OL,15,Ffollow Starmer over the edge of the
OL,16,Fcliff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
