OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778270754
OL,3,CThe post-election blame game has
OL,4,Cstarted - and Starmer is the only loser
OL,6,FI am particularly alert to the nuances
OL,7,Fof what she says, because many Labour
OL,8,FMPs and senior figures tell me that
OL,9,Fif, when the dust has settled, it is
OL,10,Fclear to them that their party is
OL,11,Fincapable of being redeemed under
OL,12,FStarmer's leadership.
OL,14,FCooper would have to take the lead -
OL,15,Fwith Ed Miliband, energy secretary,
OL,16,Fand John Heley, defence secretary -
OL,17,Finforming Starmer his time is up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
