OL,3,CThe post-election blame game has
OL,4,Cstarted - and Starmer is the only loser
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThey are seen as ministers who served
OL,12,Fin senior positions in the last Labour
OL,13,Fgovernment, as the nearest the party
OL,14,Fhas to elders, those with a duty to
OL,15,Fput party before personal advancement.
OL,17,FBut if they did serve notice on
OL,18,FStarmer, it is not at all clear he
OL,19,Fwould even hear them, let alone agree.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
