OL,3,CThe post-election blame game has
OL,4,Cstarted - and Starmer is the only loser
OL,6,FHe and his allies are going full turbo-
OL,7,Fcharged TINA (there is no alternative).
OL,9,FEven so, when you hear Starmer or
OL,10,Fthose who depend on him for their
OL,11,Fgovernment positions insist they will
OL,12,Ffight, fight, fight to win, with
OL,13,FStarmer as the unimpeachable boss,
OL,14,Fit's as well to remember he serves at
OL,15,Fthe pleasure of his MPs.
OL,17,FAnd they are worried their firm is
OL,18,Ffailing, and they will be out of a job
OL,19,Fwhen the contract is up for renewal in
OL,20,Ftwo or three years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
